                                953
                            ],
                            "spans": [
                                {
                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        811,
                                        2103,
                                        953
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "To enhance the interaction of memory slots produced by the ICAE with diverse prompts, we further fine- tune the ICAE with the PwC dataset (Prompt- with- Context), a dataset introduced in this paper consisting of thousands of (context, prompt, response) samples (as shown in Figure 1)."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 3
