                                        973,
                                        2103,
                                        1115
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Formally, the ICAE is fine- tuned for learning to encode the context into the memory slots based on which the decoder (i.e., the target LLM) can produce a desirable response "
