                                        1742,
                                        2106,
                                        1973
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Model Configuration We use the LlaMa (Touvron et al., 2023a,b) as the target LLM to test the ICAE's performance in context compression. For the encoder of the ICAE, LoRA is applied to the query and value projections of the LLM's multi- head attention. In our default setting, the memory slot length "
                                },
