                                    "bbox": [
                                        443,
                                        2158,
                                        2106,
                                        2293
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "We first evaluate the autoencoding performance of the pretrained ICAE (without instruction fine- tuning) using the following three metrics to understand how well it restores the original context from its produced memory slots: BLEU (Papineni et al., 2022), Exact- Match (EM) and cross entropy loss."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 12
